snippet.title: Location of Ancient Amber and Oil #011
snippet.description:
Irl/vlog: https://www.youtube.com/user/UCWCDXji3hdkUQsORuS?sub_confirmation=1
Gaming: https://www.youtube.com/user/UC6aWHLiYZeRJkCUBbWY?sub_confirmation=1
The location of most of the ancient amber and oil rock are Located in the winter area. Getting ancient amber in ark evolve mobile edition has three different methods to it. The first method kills an alpha dino to get more ancient amber but it can be dangerous and a flip of a coin. The Second method was fly around the map and look for a physical form of ancient amber but this can take a long time to happened due to many other player will also do it too. The last method was to watch ads for every 6 mins and you can get infinite amount of acient amber.
tags: how to get more ancient amber
